<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Bar Chart Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
Bar Chart is the simplest and most versatile of statistical diagrams. It displays horizontal bars for each point in the series and points from adjacent series are drawn as bars next to each other.
</Paragraph>



